videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza hits Gorjok Gak under the hoop who puts down a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Gak slams it down

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza dives into the scorers table while attempting to get in front of a pass.
videos.headline: Chiozza flies over scorers table

videos.description: Florida's KeVaughn Allen knocks down a deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Allen hits from deep

videos.description: Florida's Egor Koulechov hits a 3-pointer from the corner.
videos.headline: Koulechov knocks down a 3

videos.description: Egor Koulechov draws the foul while hitting a tough layup to cap off his 23-point first half.
videos.headline: Koulechov makes acrobatic layup

videos.description: After a Gorjok Gak block for Florida, Egor Koulechov hits a bank shot on the other end of the court.
videos.headline: Gak block leads to Koulechov bank shot for Gators

videos.description: Egor Koulechov speaks with Roy Philpott and Brooke Weisbrod after his 34-point performance in Florida's 116-74 win.
videos.headline: Koulechov talks about his debut game

videos.description: Grad transfer Egor Koulechov goes 6-for-9 from beyond the arc with 34 points as the No. 8 Gators rout Gardner-Webb 116-74.
videos.headline: Koulechov lights out from deep in Florida's win
